<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.4">
<l>iṭaṅkoḷ camayattai yellā meṭuttuk kaḷaivaṉa pōla</l>
<l>taṭaṅkaṭal paḷḷip perumāṉ ṟaṉṉuṭaip pūtaṅka ḷēyāy</l>
<l>kiṭantu miruntu meḻuntuṅ kītam palapala pāṭi</l>
<l>naṭantum paṟantuṅ kuṉittu nāṭakañ ceykiṉ ṟaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As if to lift up [and] remove all the creeds that take up space,</l>
<l>as the bhūtas of the great lord on a bed in the vast sea,</l>
<l>singing many many songs about [his] lying, sitting and rising,</l>
<l>walking, flying and dancing they make plays.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
